39|jstor=140639}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kenneth Kiple\">{{cite web|title=The Cambridge World History of Food|url=http://www.cambridge.org/us/books/kiple/sugar.htm|accessdate=April 1, 2014|author=Kenneth Kiple|author2=Kriemhild Conee Ornelas }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tasti\">{{cite web|title=All About Rum|url=http://www.tastings.com/spirits/rum.html|publisher=Tastings.com|accessdate=April 1, 2014}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kaufman 2008 95\u2013104\">{{cite journal|last=Kaufman|first=Cathy K.|title=Salvation in Sweetness? Sugar Beets in Antebellum America|url=https://www.academia.edu/1147323|journal=Vegetables: Proceedings of the Oxford Symposium on Food and Cookery|date=2008|pages=95\u2013104|quote=The problems with free sugar, as with most of the free labor products, were both quantitative and qualitative: free labor sugar was hard to come by, was more expensive than slave sugar, and worst of all, tasted awful.}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Robert M. Harveson\">{{cite web|title=History of Sugar Beet Production and Use|url=http://cropwatch.unl.edu/sugarbeets/sugarbeet_history|publisher=University of Nebraska|accessdate=April 1, 2014|author=Robert M. Harveson}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Magnuson 1918 68\u201379\">{{cite journal|last=Magnuson|first=Torsten A.|title=History of the Beet Sugar Industry in California|journal=Annual Publication of the Historical Society of Southern California|date=1918|volume=11|issue=1|pages=68\u201379|doi=10.2307/41168761|jstor=41168761}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"tauss\">{{cite journal|last=Taussig|first=F. W.|title=Beet Sugar and the Tariff|journal=The Quarterly Journal of Economics|date=1912|volume=26|issue=2|series=2|pages=189\u2013214|doi=10.2307/1884763|jstor=1884763}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"fiset\">{{cite journal|last=Fiset|first=Louis|title=Thinning, Topping, and Loading: Japanese Americans and Beet Sugar in World War II|journal=The Pacific Northwest Quarterly|date=1999|volume=90|series=3|pages=123\u2013139}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"buzan\">{{cite journal|last=Buzanov|first=I. F.|title=Scientific and Technical Progress in Beet Growing|journal=Vestnik Sel'skokhozyaystvennoy Nauki|date=1967|volume=13|pages=21\u201326}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"voices\">{{cite web|url=http://voices.yahoo.com/de-icing-highways-roads-using-sugar-beet-juice-5234321.html |title=De-icing Highways and Roads Using Sugar Beet Juice |publisher=[[Yahoo!]] |date= |accessdate= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"fao\">{{cite web|url=http://faostat.fao.org/site/339/default.aspx |title=Statistics |publisher=Food and Agriculture Organization |date= |access-date= |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713020710/http://faostat.fao.org/site/339/default.aspx |archive-date=2011-07-13 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"fao2\">{{cite web|title=FAOSTAT: Production, Crops, Sugar beet, 2010 data |publisher=Food and Agriculture Organization |year=2011 |url=http://faostat.fao.org/site/567/DesktopDefault.aspx?PageID=567#ancor |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114151638/http://faostat.fao.org/site/567/DesktopDefault.aspx?PageID=567 |archive-date=2013-01-14 |df= }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"sasta\">{{cite journal|title=THE EFFECTIVE COMMUNICATION OF AGRICULTURAL R&D OUTPUT IN THE UK BEET SUGAR INDUSTRY|author=Limb Re|journal=Proc South African Sugar Technology Association|year=2008|volume=81|pages=107\u2013115|url=http://www.sasta.co.za/wp-content/uploads/Proceedings/2000s/2008_%20Limb_the%20effective%20communication%20.pdf}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"farmg\">{{cite web|title=Attention to detail critical in meeting beet yield targets|publisher=Farmers Guardian|date=June 2010|url=http://www.farmersguardian.com/home/arable/arable-features/attention-to-detail-essential-in-meeting-beet-yield-targets/32671.article}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bmade\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bma-de.com/Extraktionsanlagen-fuer-Zucker.259.0.html?id=259&L=1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511194414/http://www.bma-de.com/Extraktionsanlagen-fuer-Zucker.259.0.html?id